      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW QUESTON (8) is a nine start maiden who has placed three times, the latest finishing in the minor money again when second at this track. Gave a big sight last time racing on speed much of the way. Key chance in this line up. BUSH PARTY (2) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 19 lengths sixth (27.52) last time in a Maiden at this track over 460m. Has the ability and can measure up. INSPECTION (1) makes his debut without a trial but profiles well for first outing. Worth watching for a betting move. PAW YATANA (7) is a Rebecca Gibbons-trained newcomer by Orson Allen out of Hadarah Bale. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Expected to produce a bold debut.",
